1. *Bežimo* iz ovog grada što pre! (We're escaping this city as soon as possible!)
2. Ja neću *bežati* od svojih odgovornosti. (I won't run away from my responsibilities.)
3. Da li ste *bežali* od psa kad ste videli da je lutalica? (Did you run away from the dog when you saw that it was a stray?)
4. Oni su *pobegli* kada su čuli da policija dolazi. (They fled when they heard that the police were coming.)
5. Neću *bežati* od istine, čak i ako je ona neprijatna. (I won't shy away from the truth, even if it's uncomfortable.)
6. *Beži* odavde, ne želim da te vidim! (Get out of here, I don't want to see you!)
7. Svi *beže* od tebe jer si previše zahtevan. (Everyone avoids you because you're too demanding.)
8. Kada je počela kiša, ljudi su počeli da *beže* u svoje kuće. (When it started raining, people started running to their homes.)